  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1143">
<l>uṟāatō vūraṟinta kauvai yataṉaip </l>
<l>peṟāatu peṟṟaṉṉa nīrttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I not get a rumour that is known to the (whole) town ? For what I have not got is as if I had got it (already).</l>
            </lg>
